{"tid":186110,"cid":16,"subCid":0,"title":"分享肥絲減肥餐","createTime":"2017-04-04T03:43:23.000Z","updateTime":"2019-04-28T00:13:17.000Z","uid":74299,"like":5,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"136cb4405845f854fb07ff6feee8365430dea76e","tid":186110,"uid":74299,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-04T03:43:23.000Z","msg":"肥絲減肥餐 邊個話減肥唔可以食好少少既!<br />\n要減肥唔可以虐待自己,咁先可以持之以恆<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n早餐黎,小肥絲因為返夜,所以就等於我既晚餐<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n夜晚(個餐會冇咁heavy)<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kiss.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kiss.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n 韭黃輕度炒蛋-(謎之聲:減肥你仲炒),其實減肥係可以沾少少油,但唔可以over,我呢碟菜係煮左個菜先加蛋,千祈唔好煎左隻蛋先炒埋落去<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bouncer.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 因為煎蛋既油會耗好多非常之唔健康.<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/66UN2iT.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F66UN2iT.jpg&h=cc7a0e1b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n某韓國牌子既餃-(謎之聲:d餃又高鈉又高乜乜好肥架喎)餃子好多都係唔建議食不過我會選擇呢隻餃,因為好多營養師都有推介,食9粒=1肉1穀,如果真係唔夠飽可以自選加一d菜搭夠<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"https://na.cx/i/F444fQ1.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FF444fQ1.jpg&h=542ec822&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n當然除左飲食均勻,仲要做埋健康既運動<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n利申:肥絲不專業減肥飲食分享<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/05.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n         有機會再分享一d不專業既減肥post<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/09.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4d8836033b76c33212ba6d7fb0a0b5d655f2971c","tid":186110,"uid":51858,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-04T04:11:02.000Z","msg":"隻強正呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"431bf1ae9c3f88a2f2a4a8962de90944fd951209","tid":186110,"uid":74981,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-04T04:17:39.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cf436f6029567cb12caaffca3c7f01d644ee1b40","tid":186110,"uid":74299,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-04T04:20:29.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>隻強正呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n邊度有強<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n手勢唔好隻獲冇用有微燶姐<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e855568db72108b0bdd41f06faf8a3814a4e3f80","tid":186110,"uid":74299,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-04T04:21:36.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n我叫癲兔<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/15.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 癲子你好"},{"pid":"8fea87f8b38763be8e92575f7f95fe185546143f","tid":186110,"uid":74299,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-04T04:22:23.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n我叫癲兔<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/15.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 癲<span style=\"color: red;\">狗</span>你好</blockquote>"},{"pid":"f7e1def91034b0725df623d833016f749528b520","tid":186110,"uid":26969,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-04T04:24:27.000Z","msg":"係咪有見營養師？水餃9粒一穀一肉 我知邊個brand 喎 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"06e8a8e696eafa7a98918cf1bd21ab2f42b475e9","tid":186110,"uid":29080,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-04T04:37:24.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"